name: Trickstar Fes
text: Special Summon 2 "Trickstar Tokens" (Fairy/LIGHT/Level 1/ATK 0/DEF 0). If a "Trickstar" monster(s) you control that was Special Summoned from the Extra Deck would be destroyed by battle or card effect, you can banish this card from your GY instead. You can only activate 1 "Trickstar Fes" per turn. You cannot Normal or Special Summon monsters the turn you activate this card, except "Trickstar" monsters.
